<a name=3D"8FBE688E-1E91-485B-87CB-E702707CB79A"></a>
<ul style=3D"font-family:Verdana;font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;list-style=
-type:square; margin:0; padding:0 0 13px 15px;">
<li style=3D"color:#990000;margin-top:0px;padding-top:0px;">
<font style=3D"color:#990000;">CEA and AARP partner for a look at the evolv=
ing video landscape and Americans 50 and older</font>
<br>
<font style=3D"font-family:Verdana;font-size:13px;color:#000000;font-weight=
:normal;">Americans ages 50 and older tend to spend proportionally more on =
entertainment than younger age groups. CEA's AARP-sponsored 2012 study on o=
lder American and video entertainment examines device preferences, spending=
 power and the ways retailers should appeal to this sizable segment. To see=
 more on Americans 50+ and the video landscape, check out the report: <a hr=
ef=3D"http://r.smartbrief.com/resp/ecafDlpApkeVlsxofDfJbEfCNcQI" target=3D"=
_blank">The Evolving Video Landscape</a>. <img border=3D"0" align=3D"absmid=
dle" height=3D"14" width=3D"34" src=3D"http://cdn.smartbrief.com/images/bri=
efs2/common/sm_share.gif">&thinsp;<a target=3D"_blank" href=3D"http://r.sma=
rtbrief.com/resp/ecafDlpApkeVltmUfDfJbEfCGdSw" title=3D"LinkedIn"><img src=
