<ul style=3D"font-family:Verdana;font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;list-style=
-type:square; margin:0; padding:0 0 13px 15px;">
<li style=3D"color:#990000;margin-top:0px;padding-top:0px;">
<font style=3D"color:#990000;">Gary Shapiro on Forbes.com: Consumer electro=
nics deliver music the way the artists intended</font>
<br>
<font style=3D"font-family:Verdana;font-size:13px;color:#000000;font-weight=
:normal;">Check out what CEA President and CEO, Gary Shapiro, had to say in=
 his latest column on Forbes.com! This week, Gary discusses why CEA's Audio=
 Division has joined forces with the GRAMMY Awards to create Quality Sound =
Matters, a microsite that functions as a resource for consumers and audio p=
rofessionals to learn about the wide array of technologies that make life-l=
ike digital audio possible. "The consumer electronics and entertainment ind=
ustries are in the midst of a major paradigm shift in the realm of music. T=
he primary goal of the music technology industry has historically been to m=
ake music available to consumers in a convenient medium, but that goal is i=
ncreasingly giving way to a new pursuit: delivering the absolute best sound=
 quality possible," said Shapiro. Check out and comment on the full article=
 on <a href=3D"http://r.smartbrief.com/resp/ecafDlpApkeVlsxAfDfJbEfCTqWx" t=
arget=3D"_blank">Forbes.com</a>. <img border=3D"0" align=3D"absmiddle" heig=
